name: Unidentified_Houk_(Netalych)
content:
A Houk was lived on DN-949A outpost on the planet Netalych and asked Yrica Quell and her team for help to get credits for its broken ship and leave the planet. Later the Houk helped Chass na Chadic and Kairos to find Quell.
The Houk was mentioned in the 2021 novel Shadow Fall, written by Alexander Freed.
